Alfred Hickman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alfred_Hickman 0 Alfred Hickman (25 February 1873 – 9 April 1931) was an English actor. He was married to actress Nance O'Neil. He appeared in 35 films between 1914 and 1931. Alfred_Hickman ( 25_February_1873 – 9_April_1931 ) was an_English_actor . He was_married to actress_Nance_O'Neil .
